WEBVTT

1
00:10:04.470 --> 00:10:06.220 
-没说明白  -不  说明白了
- It's not clear? - No, it's clear.

2
00:10:06.260 --> 00:10:08.560 
-我们说的是不行  -什么不行
- We're saying no. - No to what?

3
00:10:08.590 --> 00:10:11.030 
如果莉安娜接受了你的辞呈  我们也会辞职
If Leona accepts your resignations, we're resigning, too.

4
00:10:11.060 --> 00:10:12.700 
所有与热那亚事件有关系的人都会
Everyone who was involved with Genoa.

5
00:10:12.730 --> 00:10:14.600 
我不会接受你们的辞呈
I'm not going to accept your resignations.

6
00:10:14.620 --> 00:10:16.130 
恕我直言  若莉安娜接受了你的辞职
Due respect, but if Leona accepts yours,

7
00:10:16.130 --> 00:10:17.570 
就轮不到你...
you're not going to be in a position--

8
00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:19.950 
我们给你了一个坏报道  是我们的责任
We gave you a bad story. It's our responsibility.

9
00:10:19.990 --> 00:10:22.740 
这里是有原则的
There are principles of... principle here

10
00:10:22.770 --> 00:10:24.620 
有性格  有责任的
and character and responsibility.

11
00:10:24.660 --> 00:10:26.240 
你这都是从哪学来的
Who put all this in your head?

12
00:10:26.280 --> 00:10:29.050 
你啊  我们现在可以回去工作了吗
You did. Now can we go back to work?

13
00:10:33.970 --> 00:10:35.970 
你指望我哑口无言吗
You expect me to get choked up?

14
00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:37.450 
会议结束  两分钟归位
Meeting's over. Two minutes back.

